{"tid":557994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國頒發「抄襲獎」　中國產品囊括頭三名","createTime":"2018-02-12T01:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T17:56:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":200,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"eea007b8b18451530dd4982a6828a21651bc27d4","tid":557994,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:03:25.000Z","msg":"02月12日(一) 00:40   <br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180212/photo/bkncn-20180212004038009-0212_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180212004328\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180212%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180212004038009-0212_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180212004328&h=43246c29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國企業生產的「廚房多用切菜器」是抄襲德國產品。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n內地產品抄襲風氣一直為人詬病。德國反剽竊行動協會（Aktion Plagiarius）舉辦第42屆「金鼻子剽竊獎」頒獎典禮，結果中國企業的產品包辦頭三名，成為活動「最大贏家」。 <br />\n<br />\n據德國反剽竊行動協會官網消息，今年「金鼻子剽竊獎」第一名頒給了浙江溫州市平陽縣的禮品公司，該公司仿造了德國一家企業製造的廚房多用切菜器。冒牌貨甚至直接挪用正版貨牌子名稱「Genius」和產品名字「Nicer Dicer Plus」。產品外型幾乎相同到以假亂真的程度，但評審委員指出，仿冒的刀片很鈍又易斷。 <br />\n<br />\n至於第二名的大型的水上充氣公園、第三名的幼兒滑行車，正版貨生產商都是德國企業，產品均被中國企業仿冒。其中，被仿冒的德國童車品牌Puky的一名品質檢測代表指出，被仿冒的幼兒滑行車原價66歐元，但仿冒品售價僅10歐元，應該是因為仿冒貨品質低廉和做工粗糙。兩款車除了名稱之外，幾乎看不出差異。 <br />\n<br />\n參加剽竊獎頒獎典禮的律師布瑟（Aliki Busse）透露，歐盟海關在2016年，查獲6.7億歐元（約新台幣240億元）的仿冒品。他痛批剽竊傷害了原創者的利益和名譽，還用低劣的品質欺瞞消費者。 <br />\n<br />\n布瑟說，「金鼻子剽竊獎」自1977年舉辦以來都無人領獎，但宣布「得獎名單」還是有一定作用，約10%至15%的「獲獎」公司已和原創企業達成和解。"},{"pid":"b07d67897c77fe0712a3828059482dfba8692e57","tid":557994,"uid":30169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe5d7cf00ca12edf4f820f3192c1f2b8338ad6c","tid":557994,"uid":48286,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:05:32.000Z","msg":"支那又可以打飛機了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢地都冇廉恥"},{"pid":"43510477718138adced57b6217c1d876a8c6330e","tid":557994,"uid":28195,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:13:24.000Z","msg":"孔子抄襲學院"},{"pid":"5802feddd20faeb2e0107ef57da01c1dae4d9e28","tid":557994,"uid":57376,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:14:31.000Z","msg":"小心地下玻璃碎！！！"},{"pid":"1f8beee08625202ea49306a10201dc7c2c448625","tid":557994,"uid":81113,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"5802feddd20faeb2e0107ef57da01c1dae4d9e28","tid":557994,"uid":57376,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:14:31.000Z","msg":"小心地下玻璃碎！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:16:39.000Z","msg":"咪又係支那五毛工人掃返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa71976022f9247589b9247f391ff84e09de523","tid":557994,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:23:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180212/mobile/bkncn-20180212004038009-0212_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180212%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20180212004038009-0212_05011_001.html&d=CuH6vq4wStg43uexrpFrqcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=8495195c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180212/mobile/bkncn-20180212004038009-0212_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b46bddd31fab5907652b31d9bf0234b9b1224717","tid":557994,"uid":65346,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:24:41.000Z","msg":"竟然無眾泰汽車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4904c487c07d068f3cb944122bfc8d0e441f331","tid":557994,"uid":162424,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:25:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbe9aeaa8ccd2f3c709910065b6d69cb5d9465e7","tid":557994,"uid":18001,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T01:38:41.000Z","msg